=head1 SYNOPSIS

  pmarkdown < file_in.md > file_out.html_fragment

=head1 DESCRIPTION

B<pmarkdown>

=head1 OPTIONS

=over 8

=item B<--help>

Show a short help message about the program.

=item B<--helpfull>

Show the complete man page of the program.

=back

